  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8eb9d9fa0ccbe1b4cbcd2a1d889b806b, type: 3}
  m_Name: FirstDayConvo05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogue
  conversationName: FirstDayMainConversation
  lines:
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: After you use that key, you can come back to get another one from me.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: I will only be giving you one room key at a time, in accordance with our
      policy. I'm sick of people losing them, and you don't exactly look... well,
      competent.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Anyway, after you've received a key, you can enter a guest room and harvest
      materials from the guest. Then, bring the goods you harvested to the gift shop
      to sell them.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Try not to drop them, or they'll become damaged that way, too. I trust
      that even you can do something that simple without messing it up, yes?
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: If you can't carry everything you harvested, use the <b>housekeeping cart</b>
      to transport more than one product at a time to the gift shop.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: And if you haven't found it already, the gift shop is located to the right
      as you enter the hotel.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Now then, enough chatter! Get to work, the clock is ticking.
  repeatLine:
    speakerName: Randy
    line: Don't you have something else better to do?
